short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This software helps rejoin to the VRChat instance.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This software creates a WebSocket connection to VRChat in the background and records the instance information to localStorage.
You can launch VRChat or send Invite-me to rejoin instances more easily by this utility. You must be logged in to VRChat before using it.
The cookie is used for VRChat's WebSocket API and InviteMe API.
